      "para_id": "Q001780.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) Šulgi , powerful man , king of Urim , king of the four quarters : Nanna-zišagĝal , chief brewer , chief butler , chief cup-bearer , overseer of the extispicy priests , is your servant ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001780.11",
      "line_range": "11",
      "translation": "(colophon 1, 1) Seal of Nanna-zišagĝal ."
    }
